From: nss-edma-rework
Subject: [PATCH] arm64: dts: qcom: ipq8074: add ramoops pstore region

Add a 1MB ramoops reserved-memory region so kernel panics and the
console log survive a reboot. Primary crash-forensics channel on
devices without serial console access.

Based on qosmio/openwrt-ipq 0911-arm64-dts-qcom-ipq8074-add-ramoops.patch,
with console-size added to capture the full boot console log.

Signed-off-by: Julius Bairaktaris <julius@bairaktaris.de>

--- a/arch/arm64/boot/dts/qcom/ipq8074.dtsi
+++ b/arch/arm64/boot/dts/qcom/ipq8074.dtsi
@@ -198,6 +198,14 @@
 			no-map;
 			reg = <0x0 0x51000000 0x0 0x100000>;
 		};
+
+		ramoops_region: ramoops@51200000 {
+			compatible = "ramoops";
+			reg = <0x0 0x51200000 0x0 0x100000>;
+			no-map;
+			record-size = <0x1000>;
+			console-size = <0x40000>;
+		};
 	};
 
 	firmware {
